<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-24 14:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7486 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-VALUES-HNS &LR;      02-24 0494
