<P>
   GARDEN-Y2K (Undated) _ Tom Johns, the president of the
Territorial Seed Co., has no idea if the millennium bug, aka Y2K,
is ``overblown fiction or a real problem.'' But that did not stop
him from warning about possible Y2K disruptions in the catalogue
that Territorial recently mailed to 650,000 gardeners. By Barnaby
J. Feder.
</P>
