2.0-liter in-line 4, 127 horsepower at 6,000 rpm, 134 pound-feet of
torque at 3,000 rpm. &QL; 
- Transmission: &QL; 
Five-speed stick shift. &QL; 
- EPA fuel economy: &QL; 
19 city, 21 highway. &QL; 
- Highs: &QL; 
Budget price. Total upgrade. &QL; 
- Lows: &QL; 
Tight interior. No V-6 for '99. &QL;
</P>
