<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-24 20:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8139 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MUSEUM-ART-BOS &LR;      02-24 1670
